  <div class="container">
    <div class="content-full">

      <h2>Trusted by Leading Litigation Firms</h2>

      <p><a href="/about-dr-lavian/">Dr. Tal Lavian</a> provides expert witness testimony and technical consulting to law firms handling complex patent litigation and intellectual property disputes involving <a href="/communications-expert-witness/telecommunications-expert-witness/">telecommunications</a>, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/network-communications-expert-witness/">network communications</a>, Internet protocols, and related technologies. He holds a Ph.D. in Computer Science from UC Berkeley, where he spent 20 years in research and instruction at the College of Engineering.</p>

      <p>With over 35 years of industry and academic experience, Dr. Lavian has authored more than 70 expert reports, delivered over 80 depositions, and analyzed more than 200 patents across U.S. Federal and District Courts, the International Trade Commission (ITC), and the USPTO Patent Trial and Appeal Board (PTAB)&mdash;including IPRs, CBM reviews, PGRs, Ex-Parte Re-Examinations, and PTO Interferences. He has also provided testimony in international courts in Canada and Asia.</p>

      <div class="three-col law-firm-highlights">
        <div>
          <h3>Technical Expertise</h3>
          <p>Dr. Lavian&rsquo;s <a href="/communications-expert-witness/">areas of expertise</a> span the full breadth of communications technology, including telecommunications systems, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/computer-networking-expert-witness/">computer networks</a>, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/voice-over-ip-voip-expert/">VoIP</a>, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/mobile-wireless-expert/">mobile wireless</a>, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/network-security-expert-witness/">network security</a>, <a href="/communications-expert-witness/streaming-media-expert-witness/">streaming media</a>, Internet protocols, and software architecture. As an inventor on over 120 patents, he brings firsthand understanding of patent prosecution and claim construction.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Litigation Experience</h3>
          <p>Dr. Lavian has been retained across a range of high-stakes matters involving companies such as Apple, Google, Cisco, Microsoft, Amazon, Facebook, Ericsson, and T-Mobile, among <a href="/corporate-clients/">others</a>. His <a href="/cases-expert-witness-testimony/">case history</a> encompasses both plaintiff and defense engagements in patent infringement, trade secret, and other intellectual property disputes.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3>Forums &amp; Proceedings</h3>
          <p>Dr. Lavian has testified in U.S. Federal and District Courts, the ITC, and the USPTO PTAB. His experience covers claim construction and Markman hearings, jury and bench trials, depositions, and the full spectrum of post-grant proceedings. He has also provided expert opinions in international proceedings in Canada and Asia.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

